{"tid":1914192,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"韓國疫情「模範確診者」﹗記下每天生活細節終使無再人受傳染","createTime":"2020-03-07T11:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T12:24:36.000Z","uid":104138,"like":49,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5369e3857363de541216eb4d6fc4806807c3d1c1","tid":1914192,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T11:10:27.000Z","msg":"有些沒有公德心的武漢病毒肺炎確診患人，在知道自己病倒，仍要強行外出，結果把寄存在自己身上的病毒，傳播到數以百計，甚至千計的無辜者身上。<br />\n<br />\n今天韓國媒體便報導了一位被譽「模範確診者」的事例，他是在上月底在韓國仁川確診的第「1129」號確診患者。<br />\n<br />\n出於不想給別人添麻煩的心理，他在一月底懷疑自己染病後，連續 25 天每一天也會細心地記下自己的生活細節，寫了 38 頁的紀錄。而且他也盡量減少外出，避免接觸其他人，最終成功未有再感染他人，自己亦幸好痊癒。<br />\n<br />\n這位患者，據報導所說，原是從事觀光解說員。早於 1 月 23 至 26 日期間，他曾經於首爾昌德宮和景福宮等觀光地，為來自中國大陸的旅客提供現場講解工作。後來到了 2 月 1日，他開始感到喉嚨及頸部疼痛，胸口亦有點悶，便開始懷疑自己患上武漢肺炎。為了避免影響他人，他於當天起便立即申請休假，主動留在家中休息，而且每天也會用日誌，仔細記錄症狀和治療情況。<br />\n<br />\n早期他曾經向保健院求診，但由於當他並沒有發燒，而且保健院認為他未有到中國外遊紀錄，所以沒有為他做任何武漢肺炎檢測。<br />\n<br />\n後來，2 月初他亦曾經多次外出看醫生，但每次也只會去周邊的醫院。另外，為了以最大限度，減少與他人接觸的機會，他亦盡量避免乘坐巴士、地鐵等大眾交通工具，能徒步的，也會盡量走路過去，只有在需要到訪距離超過步行 1 小時以上的地方時，才會乘坐的士。<br />\n<br />\n例如他會鉅細無遺地記下每一段細節行程 - 「1 月 24 日 12 時 10 分左右在家徒步前往道禾站 ... 12 時 30 分左右乘坐地鐵，從鍾路 3 街站下車換乘 3 號線 ...」<br />\n<br />\n回到家中時，雖然他只有跟母親二人同住，但由於擔心年邁母親的健康，在家時也確切遵守疾病管理本部的健康管理方針，一直戴着衛生手套和口罩生活，餐具也會逐一每次徹底消毒。<br />\n<br />\n結果，縱然他首次進行測試時呈陰性，到了 2 月 23 日第二次檢測時才確診患上了武漢肺炎，但因為他在過去大半個月懷疑自己染病期間，一直謹慎行動，最終不單未有把病毒傳染給母親，而防疫部門也能盡早透過他的日記，準確地找出那 23 位曾經與他接觸過的人的紀錄，結果那些人亦全都未有受到感染，守住了最後防線。<br />\n<br />\n作為「模範確診者」，難怪仁川市還以他的經驗，製作了宣傳海報，表示：「如果所有疑似患者像他一樣行動，就能最大限度地減少周邊擴散的機會。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.joins.com/article/23721284\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.joins.com%2Farticle%2F23721284&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=ee66f707\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.joins.com/article/23721284</a>"},{"pid":"ebdf5ffee5b001e6bde39f8b7901f1dfa5a6a534","tid":1914192,"uid":36142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T11:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e93ad05d56c8cab7599c7e6d8edb6cd5d48dbb9","tid":1914192,"uid":183183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T11:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993aebab6275962e7d8db81aca3c9a17bb87c2ec","tid":1914192,"uid":294518,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T11:45:11.000Z","msg":"心裡想著不給別人添麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50cbdf77ebf92b062a26e98c1f7db48fcf9a2705","tid":1914192,"uid":28279,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T11:46:35.000Z","msg":"好人有好報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同支那人食退燒藥去迪士尼比真係兩個極端"},{"pid":"63e4c73b27d6026f2eb47457f0a9742002e013c7","tid":1914192,"uid":165361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T11:49:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而日本有廢老周圍走"},{"pid":"940dc3c0f88bc6f8cb5d620474f4946d31823c37","tid":1914192,"uid":193642,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T11:49:36.000Z","msg":"假到好似雷鋒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a863e52bf708e500afc21a1e41dc9e546cd47d7f","tid":1914192,"uid":34235,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T11:50:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">他開始感到喉嚨及頸部疼痛，胸口亦有點悶，便開始懷疑自己患上武漢肺炎</span><br />\n<br />\n講完我都有少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12816a3bed420b5aa1b4925c16ef54a8759e54f8","tid":1914192,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a863e52bf708e500afc21a1e41dc9e546cd47d7f","tid":1914192,"uid":34235,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T11:50:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">他開始感到喉嚨及頸部疼痛，胸口亦有點悶，便開始懷疑自己患上武漢肺炎</span><br />\n<br />\n講完我都有少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T11:50:58.000Z","msg":"記得寫日記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf534e822d9c4f81a27dc6e6ff276404a4ecc65","tid":1914192,"uid":112581,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a863e52bf708e500afc21a1e41dc9e546cd47d7f","tid":1914192,"uid":34235,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T11:50:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">他開始感到喉嚨及頸部疼痛，胸口亦有點悶，便開始懷疑自己患上武漢肺炎</span><br />\n<br />\n講完我都有少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T11:52:14.000Z","msg":"記得尋求警察協助"},{"pid":"75f6d861a7efdc78530997b691ae208cf796f34d","tid":1914192,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"940dc3c0f88bc6f8cb5d620474f4946d31823c37","tid":1914192,"uid":193642,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T11:49:36.000Z","msg":"假到好似雷鋒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T11:53:12.000Z","msg":"依個世界咩怪人都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，可能佢平時都咁記錄都冇人知"},{"pid":"dc01fed119f781240e2854c17682bc2762387ab7","tid":1914192,"uid":84043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T11:57:14.000Z","msg":"<del>未來</del>武肺日記<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5b09e5d4014f78310ecf4dc7c69803c6ca712f","tid":1914192,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T11:58:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6ab5f6de6780f27eaccc12806e72d409b393824d","tid":1914192,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T12:09:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真。自律"},{"pid":"acf68f3ae41809345689dae1a418747079ccfeb6","tid":1914192,"uid":104138,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"940dc3c0f88bc6f8cb5d620474f4946d31823c37","tid":1914192,"uid":193642,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T11:49:36.000Z","msg":"假到好似雷鋒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T12:24:36.000Z","msg":"咁又唔同，韓國透明度高咁多，一假d 記者就即刻踢爆啦<br />\n中國既制度仲衰過韓國"}]}